10
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:06,160
To be handled.

11
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:11,560
These pots need attention.

12
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,440
The clay is cracking.

13
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:16,880
Well, I can't see how a tiny splash of tea is going to help.

14
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:21,200
Sometimes you have to look hard at something to see its value.

15
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,440
See?

16
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:27,640
This one shines a little brighter.

17
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,720
I don't suppose...

18
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:31,840
Um, I mean...

19
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:34,760
I don't suppose that you want to have a drink?

20
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:40,080
Not tea, obviously. Um, in a pub, with me, tonight.

21
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,320
You wouldn't like me all that much.

22
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,720
Can I maybe decide that for myself?

23
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,680
I can't.

24
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:56,400
I'm sorry.

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,400
