39
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:01,560
Because I had a row in the shop with a chip and PIN machine.

40
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,840
You...You had a row with a machine?!

41
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:06,430
Sort of. It sat there and I shouted abuse.

42
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:06,920
Have you got cash?

43
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,360
Take my card.

44
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:14,840
You could always go yourself, you know, you've been sitting there all morning,

45
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,280
you've not even moved since I left.

46
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:21,670
And what happened about that case you were offered - the Jaria diamond?

47
00:05:21,670 --> 00:05:23,880
Not interested.

48
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:28,560
I sent them a message.

49
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,360
Don't worry about me, I can manage.

50
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:49,340


51
